CONFERENCE. Oil Imperialism? Energy and Political Power from a Global
Perspective

   Publié le 24 octobre 2016 par lauba

   capture-decran-2016-10-24-a-09-29-22
     __________________________________________________________________

   An international conference organized by Prof. Eric Bussière (Sorbonne
   University), Prof. Alain Beltran (CNRS, UMR Sirice 8138), Dr.
   Guillemette
   Crouzet (Graduate Institute of International and
   Development Studies, University of Geneva), Dr. Victor McFarland
   (University of
   Missouri) and Marta Musso (European University Institute).
   This conference has been funded by the University Paris-Sorbonne, the
   Labex
   EHNE “Ecrire une histoire nouvelle de l’Europe”, the UMR CNRS 8138 CNRS
   Sirice and the University of Missouri.
